{"tid":211790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你呢條友係海關督察？","createTime":"2017-04-22T01:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T04:41:05.000Z","uid":38047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6406a2de0e6d2190fc0a10e9278b794bbc8d9da2","tid":211790,"uid":38047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"海關督察疑因被一名男子撞到後，動怒摑對方一巴掌，又恐嚇對方的同伴稱「打X你、關你X事」，被控普通襲擊及刑事恐嚇，案件下午續審。裁判官斥被告於庭上講無聊說話，浪費法庭時間，稱「你係海關幫辦嚟，我expect（期望）你好少少㗎」。案件押至本月26日裁決。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170420/s00001/6d7707a2a0ec226860ff542d4a143c9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170420%2Fs00001%2F6d7707a2a0ec226860ff542d4a143c9b.jpg&h=a99cd186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明就係海盜嚟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e473ffb90995666180ca52e700b4eb1f87c3b19c","tid":211790,"uid":61099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:23:10.000Z","msg":"呢個人相當有可疑"},{"pid":"49800ba1b2dc63906437001516b37b124c444add","tid":211790,"uid":10334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T01:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab5ee043337592705c94b3a4888cd865ad5ef3","tid":211790,"uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/122749_236e78376b9011fbeb8fd37e1d537ab3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F122749_236e78376b9011fbeb8fd37e1d537ab3.jpg&h=f63ad629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6259a2c30f1ac9cab819c853468047e31a1dea42","tid":211790,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite